Odaily Planet Daily News According to the official announcement, Binance Futures will launch PUMPUSDT, STOUSDT and FHEUSDT perpetual contracts. Among them: 
22:30 on April 12, 2025 (Eastern Time Zone 8): PUMPUSDT perpetual contract, the maximum leverage can reach 20 times; 
22:45 on April 12, 2025 (Eastern Time Zone 8): STOUSDT perpetual contract, the maximum leverage can reach 20 times; 
23:00 on April 12, 2025 (Eastern Time Zone 8): FHEUSDT perpetual contract, the maximum leverage can reach 20 times.
